id": 102, "seek": 37760, "start": 397.28000000000003, "end": 398.52000000000004, "text": " And when?", "tokens": [51348, 400, 562, 30, 51410], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15845081418059592, "compression_ratio": 1.8409893992932862, "no_speech_prob": 0.0247146338224411}, {"id": 103, "seek": 37760, "start": 398.52000000000004, "end": 400.44, "text": " What sort of testing validation occurred?", "tokens": [51410, 708, 1333, 295, 4997, 24071, 11068, 30, 51506], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15845081418059592, "compression_ratio": 1.8409893992932862, "no_speech_prob": 0.0247146338224411}, {"id": 104, "seek": 37760, "start": 400.44, "end": 401.48, "text": " Did it work properly?", "tokens": [51506, 2589, 309, 589, 6108, 30, 51558], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15845081418059592, "compression_ratio": 1.8409893992932862, "no_speech_prob": 0.0247146338224411}, {"id": 105, "seek": 37760, "start": 401.48, "end": 406.12, "text": " And what updates are made to all the various documents that's necessary?", "tokens": [51558, 400, 437, 9205, 366, 1027, 281, 439, 264, 3683, 8512, 300, 311, 4818, 30, 51790], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15845081418059592, "compression_ratio": 1.8409893992932862, "no_speech_prob": 0.0247146338224411}, {"id": 106, "seek": 40612, "start": 406.12, "end": 407.64, "text": " There should always be documentation.", "tokens": [50364, 821, 820, 1009, 312, 14333, 13, 50440], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2141749959596446, "compression_ratio": 1.6374269005847952, "no_speech_prob": 0.0013828143710270524}, {"id": 107, "seek": 40612, "start": 407.64, "end": 410.68, "text": " It doesn't have to be overly, it doesn't have to be hundreds of pages.", "tokens": [50440, 467, 1177, 380, 362, 281, 312, 24324, 11, 309, 1177, 380, 362, 281, 312, 6779, 295, 7183, 13, 50592], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2141749959596446, "compression_ratio": 1.6374269005847952, "no_speech_prob": 0.0013828143710270524}, {"id": 108, "seek": 40